'''Sacredot''' was a title used within the [[Cult of The One and The All]] to denote a [[t'landa Til]] who was a priest of the religion.<ref name="Paradise Snare">''[[The Paradise Snare]]''</ref> They either assisted or led the ceremonies of [[Exultation]] that were held at each Colony on the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]]. During the Exultation, the Sacredot would "hum" by vibrating their chin while focusing on positive and warm emotions, which had the effect of an intoxicating drug on those who were unprepared for it. In addition, they led recruiting missions that would venture out into [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] to recruit more followers that they would then enslave.<ref name="Hutt Gambit">''[[The Hutt Gambit]]''</ref> Sacredots served the cult under the [[High Priest/Legends|High Priest]], [[Teroenza]]. [[Palazidar]] was a Sacredot, but fell asleep during an Exultation.<ref name="Paradise Snare" />

Most of them were either killed or fled into the wilderness when the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] attacked and [[Battle of Ylesia|liberated]] the planet.<ref name="TNEC">''[[The New Essential Chronology]]''</ref>

